title: Kilmar Abrego Garcia released from ICE custody. And, Indiana rejects redistricting
description: Kilmar Abrego Garcia, a man the Trump administration mistakenly deported in March and eventually returned, is now free from ICE custody. And, Indiana lawmakers reject a redistricting proposal.
